&lt;p&gt;The Surgery Division at Worthing Hospital are looking for bank staff to cover Support Secretary role. This is a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a varied role as no day is ever the same, and the post is required to cover any gaps across the General Surgery/Upper GI service. The Support Secretary provides administrative and secretarial support and applicants must be enthusiastic and able to contribute to a busy, complex division, delivering high level administrative and secretarial support to the medical teams. Excellent interpersonal and typing skills with ability to work under pressure and use own initiative is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
